snippet.title: Wheelman Fly High Trailer
snippet.description: Today Ubisoft released the "Fly High trailer to showcase the over-the-top action featured in the upcoming Wheelman video game starring film star Vin Diesel as undercover agent and expert driver for hire Milo Burick. Wheelman ships this week and will be available at retailers starting Wednesday, March 25. Wheelman will be available for the Xbox 360® video game and entertainment system from Microsoft, the PLAYSTATION®3 computer entertainment system and Windows PC and is rated "T for Teen by the ESRB.
